data.description: Come and see this beautiful house meticulously decorated, hard to  find  with more than 2000 sq feet first level, 1/4 + acre lot in a cul-de-sac. The property has a very convenient location in a great  neighborhood for a morning or evening walk with your family and pets. The lives colors will give you a happy welcome. Beautiful patio to come home and relax, fenced yard , 2 car garage with a spacious driveway. This house has plenty of windows for sunlight. Every room has been well thought. It has a combination of modern and contemporary designs. You must come and see it!
